// author: ImproperIssues (@improperissues)
I don't know why but this might just be the most useful module I've ever created with this scripting language 💀. This concept was brought over from file systems, cuz enter does indeed act like a left click in most  apps, so why not Minecraft?

def module enter-left-click
def desc "Press enter to left click, just like in the file systems!"

on key_press enter {
    input left
}
You're welcome guys.